column168: Killed his stepmother and then a year later killed the family he was living with

Time frame: Could be 1790s-1808, 1806-1809 or early 1800s.      
Cannibalism: He took body parts from his victims and he expressed a desire to eat human flesh but he never confessed to actually consuming the body parts.  
Arrest: either 1808 or 1809.   
Death: was sentenced to be broken on the wheel but was decapitated instead.
Killed at noon so church bells would hide the gunshot sounds
